# Next.js Link Component Usage

For internal navigation within the Next.js application, always use the `Link` component from `next/link` instead of a standard `<a>` tag. This enables client-side navigation and avoids unnecessary full-page refreshes, providing a better user experience.

**Do this:**
```javascript
import Link from 'next/link'

// ...

<Link href="/about">About Us</Link>
```

**Don't do this:**
```html
<a href="/about">About Us</a>
```

